title: Super Bowl LI preview
itunes:title: Super Bowl LI preview
description:
A room filled with some heroes – Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal & Marc Sessler – discuss all the latest news from around the NFL including the biggest takeaways from NFL commissioner Roger Goodell’s Super Bowl press conference, and the retirement of Colts punter Pat McAfee. Then, the heroes take a deep look at Super Bowl LI by discussing who could be a surprise star on Sunday, and also by hanging a little onion with a Super Bowl edition of “Go Get My Lunch”.
